sequenceDiagram
    participant Frontend
    participant WebSocket
    participant API
    participant Orchestrator
    participant Agents

    Frontend->>WebSocket: Connect /ws/logs
    WebSocket-->>Frontend: Connection established

    Frontend->>API: POST /api/v1/projects/{id}/run
    API->>Orchestrator: Start workflow

    loop Workflow execution
        Agents->>Orchestrator: Agent status update
        Orchestrator->>WebSocket: Emit log event
        WebSocket-->>Frontend: Stream log message
        Frontend->>Frontend: Update UI (log viewer, status board)
    end

    Orchestrator->>WebSocket: Workflow complete
    WebSocket-->>Frontend: Final status
    Frontend->>Frontend: Display completion notification